    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.1",
          "pli": "Evaṃ me sutaṃ—",
          "en": "So I have heard. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.2",
          "pli": "ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.3",
          "pli": "Tatra kho bhagavā … pe … etadavoca: ",
          "en": "There the Buddha … said: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.4",
          "pli": "“seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kūṭāgārassa yā kāci gopānasiyo sabbā tā kūṭaṅgamā kūṭasamosaraṇā kūṭasamugghātā sabbā tā samugghātaṃ gacchanti; ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, the rafters of a bungalow all lean to the peak and meet at the peak, and when the peak is demolished they’re all demolished too. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.5",
          "pli": "evameva kho, bhikkhave, ye keci akusalā dhammā sabbe te avijjāmūlakā avijjāsamosaraṇā avijjāsamugghātā, sabbe te samugghātaṃ gacchanti. ",
          "en": "In the same way any unskillful qualities are rooted in ignorance and meet in ignorance, and when ignorance is demolished they’re all demolished too. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.6",
          "pli": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: ",
          "en": "So you should train like this: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.7",
          "pli": "‘appamattā viharissāmā’ti. ",
          "en": "‘We will stay diligent.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.8",
          "pli": "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ",
          "en": "That’s how you should train.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "sn20.1:1.9",
          "pli": "Paṭhamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
